text: Tecnológico de Antioquia - University Institution (TdeA), also known as Tecnológico de Antioquia, is an institution of higher education in Colombia, located in the department of Antioquia, which offers technical training programs, technological, professional and advanced training university . Its headquarters are located in the city of Medellín. == References == * Tecnológico de Antioquia * TdeA-tv * Tecnológico de Antioquia on Twitter Category:1983 establishments in South America Category:20th-century establishments in Colombia Category:Colleges and universities in Colombia Category:Antioquia Department
